"{\"uid\": \"citizen.co.za-news-south-africa-the-thrilling-return-of-fencing-to-paris-2024-olympics-highlights-and-key-athletes-to-watch\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Home\\u00bbNews\\u00bbSouth Africa  Sponsored bySponsored  4 minute read  31 July 2024  03:34 pm  Fencing, a sport with deep historical roots, is set to dazzle audiences once again at the Paris Olympics 2024.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 86, \"end\": 93, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fencing\", \"score\": 0.999997396555251, \"rank\": 2.603449282223034e-06, \"text\": \"Fencing\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fencing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fencing\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year's competition holds special significance as it marks a century since women's fencing was first introduced at the Paris 1924 Games.\", \"from\": 197, \"to\": 337, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Grand Palais, an iconic Parisian landmark, will serve as the venue, adding a layer of grandeur and history to the event.\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 462, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fencing is not just about physical prowess; it's a sport that combines strategy, agility, and precision.\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 568, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Each bout is a dance of intellect and reflexes, with fencers using three different weapons: \\u00e9p\\u00e9e, foil, and sabre.\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 683, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Each weapon has its own rules and techniques, making fencing a diverse and dynamic sport.\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 773, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheParis Olympics 2024will feature some of the world's best fencers, each with their own unique story and style.\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 887, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lee Kiefer, representing the USA (5.20), a seasoned athlete making her fourth Olympic appearance, is one to watch in the women's foil.\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 1022, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 888, \"end\": 898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lee_Kiefer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lee Kiefer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lee_Kiefer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lee_Kiefer\"}, {\"begin\": 917, \"end\": 920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.984043027942963, \"rank\": 0.015337680264298208, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Known for her swift and precise movements, Kiefer's experience and skill make her a formidable opponent.\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another standout is Cheung Ka Long from Hong Kong, the current world champion in men's foil.\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1221, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1149, \"end\": 1163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheung_Ka_Long\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cheung Ka Long\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheung_Ka_Long\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheung_Ka_Long\"}, {\"begin\": 1169, \"end\": 1178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.9992270286502893, \"rank\": 0.0007402994387965317, \"text\": \"Hong Kong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His journey to the top has been nothing short of inspiring, with his tactical brilliance and composure under pressure setting him apart from the competition.\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1380, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The fencing schedule is packed with thrilling matches from 27 July to 4 August 2024.\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1466, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Each day promises intense competition as athletes vie for individual and team titles across the three disciplines.\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Highlights include the women's \\u00e9p\\u00e9e and men's sabre finals on 27 July, and the team events that showcase the strategic depth and camaraderie of the sport.\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1737, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Grand Palais is more than just a venue; it's a historic site that has hosted numerous significant events.\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Its majestic architecture and rich history provide the perfect backdrop for the elegance and tradition of fencing.\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1963, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This iconic location will enhance the spectator experience, making every bout a memorable spectacle.\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 2065, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fencing at theParis Olympics 2024is not just a competition; it's a celebration of history, skill, and athletic excellence.\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2189, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With a stellar lineup of athletes and the majestic Grand Palais as the venue, this event promises to be a highlight of the Games.\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2319, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether you are a long-time fan or new to the sport, the fencing events at Paris 2024 are sure to captivate and inspire.\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2441, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For those looking to add an extra layer of excitement to the Games,Easybetoffers an engaging platform to place your bets on your favourite fencers and teams.\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With real-time updates and avariety of sports bettingoptions, Easybet ensures that you stay on the edge of your seat as you witness the action unfold.\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join the thrill of the Paris Olympics and make your predictions with E